statements: SELECT * FROM voter_registration;
SELECT voter_name, voter_age FROM voter_registration WHERE voter_age > 18;
SELECT * FROM voter_registration WHERE registration_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT voter_id, voter_name FROM voter_registration ORDER BY voter_name ASC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_voters FROM voter_registration;
SELECT * FROM voter_registration WHERE voter_age > 18 ORDER BY registration_date DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT voter_id, voter_name, voter_address FROM voter_registration WHERE registration_date = '2022-01-15';
SELECT voter_name, voter_age FROM voter_registration WHERE voter_address LIKE '%Street%' ORDER BY voter_name ASC;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM voter_registration WHERE voter_age BETWEEN 18 AND 25;
SELECT DISTINCT voter_address FROM voter_registration WHERE voter_name LIKE 'J%' ORDER BY voter_address DESC;
SELECT * FROM voters;
SELECT first_name, last_name FROM voters WHERE state = 'CA';
SELECT voter_id, city, state FROM voters WHERE zip_code = '90210';
SELECT * FROM voters ORDER BY last_name ASC, first_name DESC;
SELECT voter_id, voting_frequency FROM voter_history WHERE party_affiliation = 'Independent';
SELECT * FROM voters WHERE state='NY';
SELECT first_name, last_name, address, city FROM voters WHERE zip_code='10001';
SELECT voter_id, first_name, last_name, party_affiliation FROM voters JOIN voter_history ON voters.voter_id = voter_history.voter_id WHERE voting_frequency > 5;
SELECT * FROM voters WHERE city='Los Angeles' AND state='CA';
SELECT voter_id, first_name, last_name, registration_date FROM voters JOIN voter_history ON voters.voter_id = voter_history.voter_id WHERE registration_date >= '2020-01-01';
SELECT * FROM Voter;
SELECT full_name, date_of_birth FROM Voter ORDER BY date_of_birth DESC;
SELECT voter_id, full_name, address FROM Voter WHERE address IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM VoterRegistration WHERE registration_status = 'Active';
SELECT voter_id, change_date, action_taken FROM VoterHistory ORDER BY change_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM Voter ORDER BY full_name DESC, date_of_birth ASC
SELECT full_name, address FROM Voter WHERE address IS NOT NULL
SELECT v.full_name, h.action_taken FROM Voter v JOIN VoterHistory h ON v.voter_id = h.voter_id
SELECT * FROM Voter v INNER JOIN VoterRegistration r ON v.voter_id = r.voter_id WHERE r.registration_status = 'Approved'
SELECT v.full_name, COUNT(*) AS registration_count FROM Voter v JOIN VoterRegistration r ON v.voter_id = r.voter_id GROUP BY v.voter_id HAVING registration_count > 1
SELECT * FROM voters;
SELECT first_name, last_name, email FROM voters WHERE registration_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT id, first_name, last_name, date_of_birth FROM voters ORDER BY date_of_birth DESC;
SELECT v.first_name, v.last_name, va.street_address, va.city, va.state FROM voters v JOIN voter_addresses va ON v.id = va.voter_id;
SELECT v.first_name, v.last_name, vh.registration_date, vh.last_updated, vh.status FROM voters v JOIN voter_history vh ON v.id = vh.voter_id WHERE vh.status = 'active';
SELECT * FROM voters ORDER BY last_name DESC, first_name ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT first_name, last_name, address, email FROM voters WHERE date_of_birth < '1990-01-01';
SELECT v.first_name, v.last_name, va.street_address, va.city, va.state, va.zipcode FROM voters v JOIN voter_addresses va ON v.id = va.voter_id WHERE va.state = 'CA';
SELECT v.first_name, v.last_name, vh.registration_date, vh.last_updated FROM voters v JOIN voter_history vh ON v.id = vh.voter_id WHERE vh.status = 'active' ORDER BY vh.last_updated DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT v.first_name, v.last_name, va.city, va.zipcode, va.street_address FROM voters v JOIN voter_addresses va ON v.id = va.voter_id JOIN voter_history vh ON v.id = vh.voter_id WHERE vh.status = 'inactive' AND va.state = 'NY';
SELECT * FROM Voters;
SELECT voter_name, registration_date FROM Voters ORDER BY registration_date DESC;
SELECT voter_name, age, email FROM Voters JOIN VoterDetails ON Voters.voter_id = VoterDetails.voter_id;
SELECT voter_name, total_votes FROM Voters JOIN VoterStats ON Voters.voter_id = VoterStats.voter_id WHERE total_votes > 5;
SELECT COUNT(vote_id), vote_location FROM VotingHistory GROUP BY vote_location ORDER BY COUNT(vote_id) DESC;
SELECT * FROM Voters;
SELECT voter_name, voter_address FROM Voters WHERE registration_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT v.voter_name, v.registration_date, vs.registration_status FROM Voters v JOIN VoterStatus vs ON v.voter_id = vs.voter_id;
SELECT v.voter_name, vd.age, vh.vote_date, vh.vote_location FROM Voters v JOIN VoterDetails vd ON v.voter_id = vd.voter_id JOIN VotingHistory vh ON v.voter_id = vh.voter_id;

SELECT v.voter_name, vs.is_registered, vs.registration_status, vs.registration_status, vs.registration_status, vs.registration_status FROM Voters v JOIN VoterStatus vs ON v.voter_id = vs.voter_id WHERE vs.is_registered = TRUE;
